title: Josh Kerr
description:
Whether he's punting airs in the surf or grilling on the barbie, Josh Kerr knows how to get it done.

Part of the growing Australian contingent of Arnette's Global Surf Team, Josh is a SURFER Poll award winner and aerial powerhouse who brings the fun into the water every time he paddles out.

Josh is backing the new Dibs in this clip, which have interchangeable arms (a second set comes with purchase) so you can change up your look on the fly.

Stay in touch with Arnette for giveaways, as well as new team and product updates
